title: Principles of Corporate Finance , 10/e
description:
Welcome to the Principles of Corporate Finance 10/e 

The partnership of Brealey, Myers, and Allen has produced a comprehensive and modern corporate finance textbook that continues to set the standard. With a blend of detailed analysis, comprehensive coverage, and common sense, Brealey, Myers, and Allen's Principles of Corporate Finance has earned tremendous loyalty as both a classroom tool and a professional reference work. For more details on the Tenth Edition, please visit the Information Center portion of this site.
